{"TopicId":181654,"ForumId":32,"TopicTitle":"I love the new rover MK2 Lander variant.","CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-24T21:14:02Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"MechBFP","CreatedById":184845,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-24T21:14:03Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nFor the first time yesterday, after 1,500\u002B hours of playing,\u00A0I finally made a rover that I could actually drive around without it actually flipping over or blowing up within minutes.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nPretty much all of it was thanks to the MK2 lander rover varient, the ability to change the control direction to forward, and putting a reaction wheel on it set to \u201C\u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E only\u201D with \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Stability Augmentation System\u0022\u003ESAS\u003C/abbr\u003E (usually) locked\u00A0to prograde\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI drove about 30KM in total on the Mun and successfully made it back to the ship without anyone dieing.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI may have lost 2 headlights, a solar panel, and completely 1 wheel in the process though. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe only thing I forgot to put on was some \u003Cabbr title=\u0022Reaction Control System\u0022\u003ERCS\u003C/abbr\u003E thrusters for slowing down on\u00A0those unexpected 600 meter jumps.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"septemberWaves","CreatedById":160814,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-24T22:42:17Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nThe new variant looks\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eexcellent\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0and I want to use it. On the other hand, with my current mod set I prefer other methods of building rovers; I\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ewant\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0to use it for a new lander idea I have, but\u00A0\u003Cem\u003EKerbalism\u003C/em\u003E\u00A0might make that difficult. I may have to get more creative than that to find good excuses to use it (maybe as a command point for an interplanetary transport...).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NorthernDevo","CreatedById":161219,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-27T14:13:53Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup - I totally LOVE the thing! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ERover Max is my land vehicle of choice; it\u0027s based around the MkII Rover variant.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00229AD3BB99819F5B99220E1E94BEFC4F3777F70AF9\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/959729787154258129/9AD3BB99819F5B99220E1E94BEFC4F3777F70AF9/\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThey\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ereally\u003C/em\u003E did a great job when they created the thing!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Geonovast","CreatedById":179753,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-27T14:15:50Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223529768\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181654\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221548598433\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022161219\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022NorthernDevo\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n1 minute ago, NorthernDevo said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nYup - I totally LOVE the thing! \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003ERover Max is my land vehicle of choice; it\u0027s based around the MkII Rover variant.\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003E\u003Ca href=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/959729787154258129/9AD3BB99819F5B99220E1E94BEFC4F3777F70AF9/\u0022 title=\u0022Enlarge image\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u00229AD3BB99819F5B99220E1E94BEFC4F3777F70AF9\u0022 class=\u0022ipsImage ipsImage_thumbnailed\u0022 height=\u0022576\u0022 src=\u0022https://steamuserimages-a.akamaihd.net/ugc/959729787154258129/9AD3BB99819F5B99220E1E94BEFC4F3777F70AF9/\u0022 width=\u00221024\u0022\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan\u003EThey\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Ereally\u003C/em\u003E did a great job when they created the thing!\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAww, you gave it eyebrows.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy does it always look so surprised?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"NorthernDevo","CreatedById":161219,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-27T14:20:58Z","Content":"\n\u003Cblockquote class=\u0022ipsQuote\u0022 data-ipsquote=\u0022\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentapp=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentclass=\u0022forums_Topic\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentcommentid=\u00223529769\u0022 data-ipsquote-contentid=\u0022181654\u0022 data-ipsquote-contenttype=\u0022forums\u0022 data-ipsquote-timestamp=\u00221548598550\u0022 data-ipsquote-userid=\u0022179753\u0022 data-ipsquote-username=\u0022Geonovast\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_citation\u0022\u003E\n4 minutes ago, Geonovast said:\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsQuote_contents\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAww, you gave it eyebrows.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nWhy does it always look so surprised?\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003C/div\u003E\n\u003C/blockquote\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m constantly surprised when anything I build actually\u00A0\u003Cem\u003Eworks\u003C/em\u003E. \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:D\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_cheesy.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:D\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Superfluous J","CreatedById":73725,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-27T15:23:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027ve used it several times, but never on a rover. For some reason I like the empty space to put stuff in.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI know it has doors but I like greebles.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"RealKerbal3x","CreatedById":183830,"CreatedDateTime":"2019-01-27T16:14:40Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nIt\u0027s probably my favourite revamp since 1.4. Before it was teased I was beginning to plan a Mun base and I was like \u0027oh no, how am I going to create useful rovers without a ton of mods?\u0027. Then this came along!\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Cspan style=\u0022font-size:10px;\u0022\u003Eof course, I haven\u0027t even been able to build that base yet because procrastination\u00A0\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:blush:\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_embarrassed.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:blush:\u0022\u003E\u00A0But I will get to it eventually \u003Cspan\u003E\u003Cimg alt=\u0022:P\u0022 data-emoticon=\u0022\u0022 src=\u0022//kerbal-forum-uploads.s3.us-west-2.amazonaws.com/emoticons/default_k_tongue.gif\u0022 title=\u0022:P\u0022\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/span\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}